sequenceDiagram
    participant CARD as Card<br/>Chip or NFC
    participant POS as POS Terminal
    participant GW as Payment Gateway
    participant ACQP as Acquirer Processor
    participant SW as Network Switch<br/>VisaNet or Banknet
    participant ISSP as Issuer Processor
    participant ISS as Issuing Bank

    Note over CARD,ISS: ISO 8583 Authorization Request - MTI 0100

    CARD->>POS: Card data, cryptogram, AID
    POS->>POS: Build ISO 8583 message<br/>MTI 0100 with PAN, amount,<br/>MCC, terminal ID, entry mode

    POS->>GW: Authorization request over TLS
    GW->>ACQP: Forward with gateway metadata

    ACQP->>ACQP: Validate merchant ID<br/>Check merchant status<br/>Append acquirer BIN

    ACQP->>SW: Route based on card BIN<br/>4xxx to VisaNet<br/>51-55xx to Banknet

    SW->>SW: Validate message format<br/>Identify issuer from BIN table<br/>Run fraud scoring in under 1ms<br/>Append risk score to message

    SW->>ISSP: Forward to issuer processor
    ISSP->>ISS: Apply issuer decision rules

    ISS->>ISS: Check account status<br/>Verify available balance or credit<br/>Run fraud models<br/>Check velocity limits<br/>Validate EMV cryptogram

    Note over CARD,ISS: ISO 8583 Authorization Response - MTI 0110

    ISS-->>ISSP: Decision plus response code<br/>Approval code if approved
    ISSP-->>SW: Response with auth code
    SW-->>SW: Log transaction<br/>Append network reference ID
    SW-->>ACQP: Forward response
    ACQP-->>GW: Response with auth code
    GW-->>POS: Authorization result
    POS-->>CARD: Display approved or declined

    Note over CARD,ISS: Total round trip typically 1-3 seconds end to end
